## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of mobile banking app security. The findings are subject to the limitations of the sources used, which may not reflect the most recent developments in cybersecurity. Additionally, user experiences and security practices can vary widely, influencing the overall safety of mobile banking apps.